1. USER EXPERIENCE (FIRST 60 SECONDS)

This is where most ideas die—you’re going to win here.

Onboarding Flow (Dead Simple)
	1.	Connect Data Sources
	•	Apple Health
	•	Google / browsing
	•	Purchase history
	•	Fitness apps
	•	Social (optional)
	•	Manual inputs (high-value niche)
